    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When taken into the body or bloodstream, the poison inflicts the Poison status effect. The target must immediately attempt a DV13 Resist Torture/Drugs Check (use Physical for mooks) if they are susceptible to poison. On fail, they take 2d6 damage directly to their HP. Lasts for 10 triggers/10 rounds/5 minutes, or until an antidote is administered. Each new poison application refreshes the timer, but the damage does not stack with itself. Stacks with Biotoxin. Does not cause a sleeping target to wake.</p>"
